## ⚙️ How It Works


Your Location: Miami (Florida) Card Billing Address: California Order: Shopify checkout

ROUTING:

    You initiate payment in Miami
    Configuration intercepts payment domains
    Routes to California proxy node
    Payment processor sees California IP
    California matches billing address ✅
    Fraud detection sees accurate card data ✅
    Transaction approved instantly ✅

