## 🧪 Testing (Do This First!)

### Test 1: Verify IP Location (Free)
1. Enable config in Shadowrocket
2. Open Safari
3. Go to https://iplocation.io
4. Confirm IP shows your billing state (CA/TX/FL/NY)

### Test 2: $1 Charge Test
1. Visit any US store (Shopify, WooCommerce, etc.)
2. Add $1 item to cart
3. Enable Shadowrocket
4. Checkout with your card
5. Expected: ✅ **Order approved**

### Test 3: Full Checkout
1. Process $5-10 test order
2. Verify no extra verification needed
3. Check order confirmation received
4. Ready for real supplier orders!

